New Records: Mitchell Starc took 3-50, his best ODI figures in 2024
Adil Rashid claimed his 200th ODI wicket
Key Match Events: Mitchell Starc pinned Harry Brook lbw with a brilliant delivery
Aaron Hardie claimed two wickets in two balls
Jamie Smith and Jacob Bethell stopped the bleeding with a stand of 55
Mitchell Marsh and Marnus Labuschagne took them to 145 for 3
Alex Carey played smartly as he took singles late in an over to protect Josh Hazlewood
Mitchell Marsh flicked a switch with two sixes in three balls off the struggling Carse
Post-Match Reflections: England's lower order showed there were few demons in the surface
Miscellaneous Highlights: Australia welcomed back Josh Hazlewood and Mitchell Starc from illness
The Test duo would finish with five wickets between them
The game was just about done when Jamie Smith clipped Josh Hazlewood to midwicket for a very neat 49
Others: England captain Harry Brook was beaten for pace by Mitchell Starc's searing inswinging yorker
